summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the City Treasurer to cancel unpaid assessments levied for the improvement of Murray Avenue, et al., by trunk sewer, Local Improvement District No. 3402, on portion of Southwest one-quarter of Northeast one-quarter of Section twenty-six (26), Township twenty-four (24) North, Range three (3) East, W.M., which has been deeded to the City of Seattle for street purposes.
